<dl><dt>
<a href="../list.html#LMS"><img src="../Common/LMS.gif" name="Graphic4" align="bottom" border="2" height="45" hspace="5" width="45"></a>
<b><i>Mario Huys:</i> <a href="LMS/lms_rome.html">Last Man Standing: Operation Rome</a></b>
</dt><dd style="margin-bottom: 0.2in;">
Order a pizza, and solve a puzzle fit for any <em>piazza.</em>
</dd></dl>

<dl><dt>
<a href="../list.html#Machiavelli"><img src="../Common/Machiavelli.gif" name="Graphic4" align="bottom" border="2" height="45" hspace="5" width="45"></a>
<b><i>Kevin Burt:</i> <a href="Burt/MostMoralMan.html">A Most Moral Man</a></b>
</dt><dd style="margin-bottom: 0.2in;">
Surely he can't be referring to "Old Nick" &#8212; the Devil himself!
</dd></dl>

<dl><dt>
<a href="../list.html#Peeriblah"><img src="../Common/History.gif" name="Graphic4" align="bottom" border="2" height="45" hspace="5" width="45"></a>
<b><i>Larry Peery:</i> <a href="Peery/defeat.html">Peeriblah Goes Down to Defeat</a></b>
</dt><dd style="margin-bottom: 0.2in;">
Another course of Szechuan-American diplomacy is served.  Will we be hungry again in an hour?
</dd></dl>

